WEBVTT


00:01:24.900 --> 00:01:27.786
[Episode 6: Yu Lei, I believe in you...]

00:01:40.554 --> 00:01:42.782
- What are you doing here?
- What are you doing here?

00:01:58.640 --> 00:01:59.719
I'm sorry.

00:01:59.719 --> 00:02:02.079
- You...
- "You" what?

00:02:02.079 --> 00:02:05.099
- I...
- "I" what?

00:02:06.799 --> 00:02:09.159
I already apologized.

00:02:09.159 --> 00:02:12.120
I-If there's anything you want me to do
to make it up to you,

00:02:12.120 --> 00:02:13.959
just tell me.

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:16.800
Forget it.

00:02:16.800 --> 00:02:18.439
We're all adults here.

00:02:18.439 --> 00:02:19.919
It's not a big deal.

00:02:19.919 --> 00:02:22.280
I didn't take it to heart.

00:02:22.280 --> 00:02:26.080
Wait. So we're just going to
leave it at that?

00:02:26.080 --> 00:02:27.840
What else?

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:30.240
We just had too much to drink.

00:02:30.240 --> 00:02:34.759
Anyway, I'll just pretend
I don't remember anything.

00:02:34.759 --> 00:02:37.399
And you should stop pestering me about it.

00:02:43.155 --> 00:02:45.714
Who's pestering you?

00:03:01.360 --> 00:03:02.986
Yu Lei.

00:03:02.986 --> 00:03:04.786
What's wrong?

00:03:06.185 --> 00:03:07.985
I'm fine.

00:03:08.738 --> 00:03:11.498
I'm just going to go for a walk by myself.

00:03:30.679 --> 00:03:33.079
Chen Ke, you...

00:03:33.079 --> 00:03:35.879
Excuse me. I thought you were someone else.

00:03:46.320 --> 00:03:47.359
Chen Ke.

00:03:47.359 --> 00:03:49.239
Where were you last night?

00:03:49.239 --> 00:03:51.320
I was looking for you all night.

00:03:51.320 --> 00:03:53.753
Why didn't you answer
any of my calls or texts?

00:03:53.753 --> 00:03:56.920
Your roommate also said
he didn't know where you went.

00:03:56.920 --> 00:04:00.040
Last night,
I just wanted some quiet time alone.

00:04:00.040 --> 00:04:02.160
And my phone happened to run of of battery.

00:04:02.160 --> 00:04:03.960
You don't have to worry.

00:04:05.920 --> 00:04:07.880
How could I not be worried?

00:04:07.880 --> 00:04:11.079
If I couldn't find you,
I was about to call the police.

00:04:11.079 --> 00:04:14.160
You were that worried
that you couldn't find me?

00:04:14.160 --> 00:04:16.080
Of course.

00:04:16.080 --> 00:04:18.447
You're my best friend.

00:04:20.319 --> 00:04:25.005
Then Ouyang Han isn't your best friend?

00:04:25.005 --> 00:04:26.759
He...

00:04:26.759 --> 00:04:28.359
I guess so.

00:04:28.359 --> 00:04:32.600
But he and I... We're... We're different.

00:04:32.600 --> 00:04:34.080
What about Li Ming?

00:04:34.080 --> 00:04:36.799
He's your best friend too, right?

00:04:37.520 --> 00:04:38.960
Yu Lei.

00:04:38.960 --> 00:04:41.439
You have so many "best friends".

00:04:41.439 --> 00:04:45.280
Among them, I guess I'm just one of many.

00:04:45.280 --> 00:04:47.319
No. It's not like that, Ke Ke.

00:04:47.319 --> 00:04:48.480
Let me explain.

00:04:48.480 --> 00:04:50.600
- With them, I'm just...
- Forget it.

00:04:50.600 --> 00:04:52.799
I don't want to fight with you.

00:04:52.799 --> 00:04:55.400
The orchestra has a performance
in a couple of days.

00:04:55.400 --> 00:04:59.160
If there's anything,
let's talk about it after the show.

00:05:25.319 --> 00:05:27.480
June 2, 2001.

00:05:27.480 --> 00:05:29.520
Cloudy.

00:05:29.520 --> 00:05:31.920
I thought he would turn back.

00:05:31.920 --> 00:05:33.799
But he didn't.

00:05:34.960 --> 00:05:38.799
Maybe his world is bigger without me.

00:05:38.799 --> 00:05:41.239
If that's the case...

00:05:41.239 --> 00:05:46.039
what's the point of keeping the music
that I wrote for him?

00:05:54.879 --> 00:05:56.920
Okay. Next.

00:05:56.920 --> 00:05:59.200
Let's see what else they have.

00:06:06.480 --> 00:06:07.679
Next.

00:06:07.679 --> 00:06:09.400
Hey, buddy. It's your turn.

00:06:09.400 --> 00:06:11.359
It's your turn.

00:06:11.359 --> 00:06:12.955
Ma'am, two chicken legs.

00:06:12.955 --> 00:06:14.799
No, no. Just one is fine.

00:06:14.799 --> 00:06:16.599
So how many is it?

00:06:49.199 --> 00:06:50.160
What's wrong?

00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:52.320
Wrestling with yourself again?

00:06:53.160 --> 00:06:55.957
Senior. I...

00:06:55.957 --> 00:06:57.920
I know the performance is coming up,

00:06:57.920 --> 00:07:00.375
but there's no need
to put so much pressure on yourself.

00:07:00.375 --> 00:07:01.600
Relax.

00:07:01.600 --> 00:07:03.400
Have something to eat.

00:07:05.040 --> 00:07:06.999
I'll leave you to it.

00:07:06.999 --> 00:07:08.799
Thanks, senior.

00:07:27.640 --> 00:07:29.960
What's up with you two now?

00:07:29.960 --> 00:07:31.520
Sis.

00:07:31.520 --> 00:07:33.480
Nothing's wrong.

00:07:33.480 --> 00:07:34.840
Nothing?

00:07:34.840 --> 00:07:38.599
Then why do you have to give him food
through me?

00:07:39.759 --> 00:07:42.759
I just don't want to
affect his performance.

00:07:55.319 --> 00:07:58.039
- Give me the shampoo.
- Here.

00:08:00.160 --> 00:08:02.039
Did you bring soap?

00:08:03.559 --> 00:08:05.359
You can use mine.

00:08:42.400 --> 00:08:45.199
Well... I'm just here to give my sister
some documents.

00:08:45.199 --> 00:08:48.319
Is your rehearsal going well?

00:08:48.319 --> 00:08:49.640
Yeah.

00:08:50.439 --> 00:08:52.680
Hurry up. We're running out of time.

00:09:01.400 --> 00:09:04.880
Do you have something else to say to me?

00:09:06.040 --> 00:09:08.040
I hope your performance goes well.

00:09:08.040 --> 00:09:09.760
Thanks.

00:09:09.760 --> 00:09:11.377
Anything else?

00:09:13.280 --> 00:09:15.839
- Well, I...
- Chen Ke, it's time for rehearsal.

00:09:15.839 --> 00:09:17.444
Okay.

00:09:44.679 --> 00:09:46.599
Very good. Everyone's in great shape.

00:09:46.599 --> 00:09:48.719
I hope you can keep it up
for the actual performance.

00:09:48.719 --> 00:09:50.759
Thanks, senior.

00:09:56.789 --> 00:09:59.005
[Olympic Theme Memorial Recital]

00:10:06.719 --> 00:10:08.170
Chen Ke.

00:10:09.040 --> 00:10:10.360
Senior.

00:10:10.360 --> 00:10:11.479
Why are you here all by yourself?

00:10:11.479 --> 00:10:13.000
Not celebrating with everyone?

00:10:13.000 --> 00:10:14.079
It's nothing.

00:10:14.079 --> 00:10:16.520
I was just here to fill in
for the original pianist.

00:10:16.520 --> 00:10:18.280
I don't really know everyone that well.

00:10:18.280 --> 00:10:20.359
It's better if I don't go.

00:10:21.040 --> 00:10:23.400
Ta-da.

00:10:23.400 --> 00:10:24.760
We couldn't have done it
without you this time.

00:10:24.760 --> 00:10:26.599
Our performance went so smoothly
because of you.

00:10:26.599 --> 00:10:28.640
Since you don't want to
celebrate with everyone,

00:10:28.640 --> 00:10:30.799
I'll have a drink with you here.

00:10:30.799 --> 00:10:32.400
Senior, I...

00:10:32.400 --> 00:10:34.999
Come on. Here's to you.

00:10:45.719 --> 00:10:47.520
Chen Ke.

00:10:47.520 --> 00:10:51.319
Actually, these past few days,
I've been watching you.

00:10:51.319 --> 00:10:55.439
Even though you've been focusing on
practicing with the orchestra,

00:10:55.439 --> 00:10:57.350
and seem no different than usual,

00:10:57.350 --> 00:11:01.280
but I can tell that
compared to when I first met you,

00:11:01.280 --> 00:11:03.840
you're in a very different state of mind.

00:11:05.559 --> 00:11:08.399
Senior. You're overthinking it.

00:11:10.000 --> 00:11:12.679
Your mood has been going up and down

00:11:12.679 --> 00:11:15.079
all because of Yu Lei, isn't it?

00:11:20.400 --> 00:11:21.839
Chen Ke.

00:11:21.839 --> 00:11:23.920
You don't have to answer me right away.

00:11:23.920 --> 00:11:27.440
Can you first listen to what I have to say?

00:11:28.920 --> 00:11:32.199
From the first time
I saw you play the piano,

00:11:32.199 --> 00:11:33.920
I've really admired you.

00:11:33.920 --> 00:11:35.959
I felt like I'd met a kindred spirit.

00:11:35.959 --> 00:11:38.880
And I wanted to get closer to you.

00:11:38.880 --> 00:11:41.360
You're a wonderful guy.

00:11:41.360 --> 00:11:47.280
Besides admiration,
I think I might also like you a little.

00:11:47.280 --> 00:11:52.559
But I gradually realized
that your heart doesn't open up so easily.

00:11:52.559 --> 00:11:56.960
But Yu Lei seems to have done it.

00:12:01.880 --> 00:12:04.520
It's rare to find a true friend in life.

00:12:04.520 --> 00:12:08.920
I'm happy for Yu Lei that he has you
as such a good friend.

00:12:08.920 --> 00:12:13.074
I just wonder
if you two have realized it yourselves.

00:12:13.074 --> 00:12:16.959
Maybe the feelings and bond
between you and him

00:12:16.959 --> 00:12:20.479
go beyond what it means
to be just good friends.

00:12:22.959 --> 00:12:27.400
On your birthday,
I saw all of Yu Lei's reactions.

00:12:27.400 --> 00:12:30.199
And you've repeatedly been unsettled
because of Yu Lei.

00:12:30.199 --> 00:12:31.999
What does that tell you?

00:12:33.280 --> 00:12:36.440
Senior, I don't get it.

00:12:37.160 --> 00:12:40.360
This just shows that between you and Yu Lei,

00:12:40.360 --> 00:12:42.160
there's no room for anyone else.

00:12:42.160 --> 00:12:43.959
Including me.

00:12:43.959 --> 00:12:47.679
So even if I used to have a crush on you,

00:12:47.679 --> 00:12:49.040
it was one-sided.

00:12:49.040 --> 00:12:51.160
It could never be a two-way street.

00:12:51.160 --> 00:12:54.359
But you and Yu Lei have a real shot.

00:12:55.520 --> 00:12:58.559
But does Yu Lei feel the same way?

00:12:58.559 --> 00:13:00.800
He has so many friends.

00:13:02.255 --> 00:13:04.667
Am I really the most important one to him?

00:13:06.599 --> 00:13:12.000
At this moment,
I've never faced a problem like this before.

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:14.239
I have no idea how to solve it.

00:13:14.970 --> 00:13:17.319
Forget about what Yu Lei is thinking.

00:13:17.319 --> 00:13:22.759
Right now,
I can't even figure out my own feelings.

00:13:25.360 --> 00:13:27.280
Chen Ke.

00:13:27.280 --> 00:13:33.000
If you think about it, life is a long journey.

00:13:33.000 --> 00:13:36.319
Walking it alone would be far too lonely.

00:13:36.319 --> 00:13:39.520
That's why we always hope
to find a traveling companion

00:13:39.520 --> 00:13:42.479
to walk with us, step by step.

00:13:42.479 --> 00:13:44.637
If you're lucky enough,

00:13:44.637 --> 00:13:48.959
you'll meet someone
who can see into the depths of your soul.

00:13:48.959 --> 00:13:50.666
In an encounter like that,

00:13:50.666 --> 00:13:53.280
you'll feel something
you've never felt before.

00:13:53.280 --> 00:13:56.479
A feeling of being cherished,
of being treasured.

00:13:57.799 --> 00:14:01.520
It's a feeling like
the entire universe is cheering you on.

00:14:01.520 --> 00:14:03.599
And every one of us needs that feeling

00:14:03.599 --> 00:14:07.079
of being validated, of being seen,
of being needed.

00:14:07.079 --> 00:14:09.679
You chasing Lei Lei, Lei Lei chasing you...

00:14:09.679 --> 00:14:11.479
it's all the same.

00:14:12.360 --> 00:14:14.640
But...

00:14:14.640 --> 00:14:16.880
does Yu Lei feel the same way?

00:14:16.880 --> 00:14:20.079
He has so many friends.

00:14:20.079 --> 00:14:22.680
Am I really the most important one to him?

00:14:23.640 --> 00:14:24.839
Chen Ke.

00:14:24.839 --> 00:14:27.520
You have to understand, Lei Lei and I
have been close since we were kids.

00:14:27.520 --> 00:14:30.273
He might seem carefree, but deep down,

00:14:30.273 --> 00:14:32.833
he's a very sensitive and gentle person.

00:14:34.360 --> 00:14:36.799
But when it comes to someone he likes,

00:14:36.799 --> 00:14:39.719
he always does things that are thoughtful,

00:14:39.719 --> 00:14:42.173
but also completely baffling.

00:14:42.920 --> 00:14:45.319
And he only confesses his reasons
at the very end.

00:14:45.319 --> 00:14:49.839
And I think you two are quite similar.

00:14:49.839 --> 00:14:52.400
So the way you two
keep avoiding each other

00:14:52.400 --> 00:14:54.520
and second-guessing everything,
it's just exhausting.

00:14:54.520 --> 00:14:59.799
Maybe you could find a way
to let Lei Lei know how you feel.

00:14:59.799 --> 00:15:02.000
Like, for example...

00:15:02.000 --> 00:15:03.394
Like what?

00:15:05.102 --> 00:15:07.280
Like preparing a special gift or something.

00:15:07.280 --> 00:15:09.400
Of course, I'm just guessing here.

00:15:09.400 --> 00:15:12.679
What you actually do is up to you.

00:15:12.679 --> 00:15:14.520
Okay. Thanks, senior.

00:15:14.520 --> 00:15:16.437
I know what to do now.

00:15:18.319 --> 00:15:19.880
Wait.

00:15:19.880 --> 00:15:22.079
Hey, I had a crush on you for a bit.

00:15:22.079 --> 00:15:23.880
Can't you at least give me
some kind of reaction?

00:15:23.880 --> 00:15:26.337
You're making me lose face here.

00:15:47.400 --> 00:15:49.520
July 12, 2001.

00:15:49.520 --> 00:15:51.079
Sunny.

00:15:51.079 --> 00:15:53.439
My world suddenly opened up.

00:15:53.439 --> 00:15:55.760
I wanted to run. I wanted to scream.

00:15:55.760 --> 00:15:59.792
I wanted to, in the very next second,
shout my feelings out loud.

00:15:59.792 --> 00:16:02.040
But in the next second,
[Countdown to Beijing's Bid for Olympics]

00:16:02.040 --> 00:16:04.720
my world turned to gray.
[1 Day Left]

00:16:08.839 --> 00:16:10.599
Hello?

00:16:10.599 --> 00:16:12.440
Mom?

00:16:13.799 --> 00:16:14.839
Lin Wen.

00:16:14.839 --> 00:16:17.000
Why did the lunch lady give you
so much meat for dinner?

00:16:17.000 --> 00:16:18.400
That's not fair!

00:16:18.400 --> 00:16:20.559
Good students get more meat.
What's wrong with that?

00:16:20.559 --> 00:16:22.160
So good students get to eat more meat?

00:16:22.160 --> 00:16:23.601
Yep.

00:16:26.559 --> 00:16:28.000
Yu Lei!

00:16:28.000 --> 00:16:29.880
Dude! Why are you in here
with the lights off?

00:16:29.880 --> 00:16:32.080
You scared me to death!

00:16:38.160 --> 00:16:39.959
Shoot. I overslept.

00:16:39.959 --> 00:16:41.839
Is the school orchestra's performance over?

00:16:41.839 --> 00:16:44.800
Dude, it ended a long time ago.

00:16:46.040 --> 00:16:48.240
Did you guys see Chen Ke then?

00:16:48.240 --> 00:16:49.549
Nope.

00:16:55.479 --> 00:16:58.158
Ke Ke. You're back. I...

00:16:58.967 --> 00:17:00.439
Wait. What's wrong with you?

00:17:00.439 --> 00:17:03.160
I... I just got a call from my mom.

00:17:03.160 --> 00:17:07.239
She said my dad
had a sudden medical emergency.

00:17:07.239 --> 00:17:09.999
Ke Ke, try not to worry too much.

00:17:09.999 --> 00:17:11.199
Your dad isn't that old.

00:17:11.199 --> 00:17:12.999
He should be in decent health.

00:17:12.999 --> 00:17:14.560
They got him to the hospital quickly,

00:17:14.560 --> 00:17:16.640
so I'm sure it's nothing too serious.

00:17:16.640 --> 00:17:18.719
My dad has always had high blood pressure.

00:17:18.719 --> 00:17:21.175
Two years ago, he was diagnosed
with coronary heart disease.

00:17:21.920 --> 00:17:23.519
But I was preparing for
my college entrance exams then,

00:17:23.519 --> 00:17:24.999
so my family kept it from me.

00:17:24.999 --> 00:17:26.640
I only just found out about it now.

00:17:26.640 --> 00:17:29.080
For the past six months,
my dad's been having frequent angina attacks.

00:17:29.080 --> 00:17:31.600
And now it's turned into a heart attack.

00:17:32.439 --> 00:17:34.680
Here, here. Drink some water first.

00:17:35.400 --> 00:17:38.439
Ke Ke, when our parents get to this age,

00:17:38.439 --> 00:17:39.999
it's common for them to get sick.

00:17:39.999 --> 00:17:42.079
Don't blame yourself too much.

00:17:42.999 --> 00:17:44.999
How can I not blame myself?

00:17:44.999 --> 00:17:47.719
No matter what, he's my dad.

00:17:47.719 --> 00:17:51.640
I had no idea his health had gotten this bad.

00:17:58.880 --> 00:18:01.279
Hello? Mom?

00:18:01.279 --> 00:18:02.400
How's Dad?

00:18:02.400 --> 00:18:04.800
For now, he's out of immediate danger.

00:18:04.800 --> 00:18:08.920
Son. I need to discuss something with you.

00:18:08.920 --> 00:18:12.439
The doctor said your dad
needs another operation.

00:18:12.439 --> 00:18:16.600
But for this hospital, I'm afraid they can't
perform such a difficult one.

00:18:16.600 --> 00:18:18.679
Then what about transferring him
to the provincial capital?

00:18:18.679 --> 00:18:20.840
Or a major hospital in Beijing or Shanghai?

00:18:20.840 --> 00:18:22.360
Could they do it there?

00:18:22.360 --> 00:18:24.960
They could, but I'm worried.

00:18:24.960 --> 00:18:26.719
The long journey would be hard on your dad.

00:18:26.719 --> 00:18:29.360
I'm afraid he might not make it through.

00:18:29.360 --> 00:18:32.039
Son, I'm so overwhelmed right now.

00:18:32.039 --> 00:18:34.239
Can you help me decide what to do?

00:18:34.239 --> 00:18:37.039
Why don't we just transfer him?

00:18:37.039 --> 00:18:38.805
We have to take the chance.

00:18:39.519 --> 00:18:41.999
No. We can't.

00:18:41.999 --> 00:18:43.960
Dad's condition...

00:18:44.679 --> 00:18:48.239
Mom, let's both think it over some more.

00:18:48.239 --> 00:18:49.640
There has to be a way.

00:18:49.640 --> 00:18:51.479
Okay. You try not to panic, either.

00:18:51.479 --> 00:18:54.880
Don't worry. The doctor said
your dad should be fine tonight.

00:18:54.880 --> 00:18:56.519
They'll keep him under observation.

00:18:56.519 --> 00:18:57.959
We can wait until tomorrow

00:18:57.959 --> 00:19:00.559
to make a decision based on his condition.

00:19:01.279 --> 00:19:03.079
Okay.

00:19:04.600 --> 00:19:07.439
Ke Ke. My mom used to work at a hospital.

00:19:07.439 --> 00:19:09.640
She knows a lot of really good doctors.

00:19:09.640 --> 00:19:11.160
I'm sure she can help.

00:19:11.160 --> 00:19:13.640
Besides, modern medicine is so advanced now.

00:19:13.640 --> 00:19:15.600
I'm sure they can do something.

00:19:15.600 --> 00:19:17.880
So don't worry too much.

00:19:17.880 --> 00:19:19.080
Yu Lei.

00:19:19.080 --> 00:19:20.519
Thank you for being here with me.

00:19:20.519 --> 00:19:22.279
I feel much better.

00:19:22.279 --> 00:19:26.479
But just standing here and doing nothing
is unbearable.

00:19:26.479 --> 00:19:28.959
So, what are you going to do?

00:19:28.959 --> 00:19:31.320
I'm going to find my advisor now
and ask for leave.

00:19:31.320 --> 00:19:33.680
And book the next flight home.

00:19:34.600 --> 00:19:37.160
But final exams are coming up.

00:19:37.160 --> 00:19:39.680
I can't worry about that right now.

00:19:49.080 --> 00:19:50.279
There's no way I'm letting you go alone.

00:19:50.279 --> 00:19:52.519
I wouldn't be able to rest easy.

00:19:52.519 --> 00:19:55.080
I'm booking tickets for both of us right now.

00:19:55.080 --> 00:19:56.759
Both of us?

00:19:56.759 --> 00:19:58.519
I've made up my mind.

00:19:58.519 --> 00:20:01.680
I'm skipping the exams too.
I'm going back with you.

00:20:25.318 --> 00:20:27.506
[Department of Internal Medicine]

00:20:33.160 --> 00:20:36.800
Ke Ke. Talk to your dad.

00:20:36.800 --> 00:20:38.120
Dad.

00:20:38.120 --> 00:20:41.640
Are you feeling any better?

00:20:41.640 --> 00:20:42.840
I'm fine.

00:20:42.840 --> 00:20:44.479
I'm perfectly healthy.

00:20:44.479 --> 00:20:46.839
What's a little sickness like this?

00:20:47.600 --> 00:20:48.880
Final exams are coming up.

00:20:48.880 --> 00:20:50.439
And you came all the way back.

00:20:50.439 --> 00:20:52.800
Are you just throwing away your grades?

00:20:52.800 --> 00:20:53.840
And you.

00:20:53.840 --> 00:20:56.160
Always making a big fuss over nothing.

00:20:56.920 --> 00:20:59.279
Sir, you shouldn't say that about Chen Ke.

00:20:59.279 --> 00:21:01.039
He was just worried about you.

00:21:01.039 --> 00:21:03.479
The moment he heard you were sick,
he was so anxious.

00:21:03.479 --> 00:21:06.039
He bought a ticket and flew back overnight.

00:21:06.039 --> 00:21:08.279
On the way here, he told me

00:21:08.279 --> 00:21:10.279
that he felt bad for not spending
enough time with you during winter break.

00:21:10.279 --> 00:21:12.519
He really regrets it.

00:21:13.800 --> 00:21:15.920
Isn't that right, Chen Ke?

00:21:15.920 --> 00:21:17.080
Yeah.

00:21:17.080 --> 00:21:19.840
Besides, we've already spoken
to our professor and made arrangements.

00:21:19.840 --> 00:21:22.920
He said we can take the make-up exams
at the beginning of next semester.

00:21:22.920 --> 00:21:24.719
It won't affect our grades.

00:21:24.719 --> 00:21:27.559
Sir, Ma'am, you don't have to worry.

00:21:28.239 --> 00:21:29.640
Really?

00:21:29.640 --> 00:21:31.439
- Really.
- See?

00:21:31.439 --> 00:21:33.080
The boy is just trying to be a good son.

00:21:33.080 --> 00:21:34.479
And he's thought everything through.

00:21:34.479 --> 00:21:36.880
Why are you still looking so grim?

00:21:38.560 --> 00:21:40.320
Alright, alright.

00:21:40.320 --> 00:21:41.800
Let's eat first.

00:21:41.800 --> 00:21:42.999
The congee is getting cold.

00:21:42.999 --> 00:21:44.479
It's not like I can't move.

00:21:44.479 --> 00:21:47.920
- Here.
- Mom, let me do it.

00:21:48.719 --> 00:21:50.880
Let your son feed you.

00:22:04.479 --> 00:22:07.719
Mom, you've been at the hospital all day.

00:22:07.719 --> 00:22:08.920
If you keep pushing yourself like this,

00:22:08.920 --> 00:22:10.640
you might end up
in a hospital bed yourself.

00:22:10.640 --> 00:22:12.999
Don't worry. I'm here.

00:22:12.999 --> 00:22:14.279
That's right, Ma'am.

00:22:14.279 --> 00:22:16.160
I'm here to help Ke Ke take care of him.

00:22:16.160 --> 00:22:19.439
You should go home
and get a good night's sleep.

00:22:19.439 --> 00:22:22.440
If only I could actually rest easy.

00:22:26.160 --> 00:22:27.640
Hello? Mom?

00:22:27.640 --> 00:22:28.800
Son.

00:22:28.800 --> 00:22:30.080
I have great news.

00:22:30.080 --> 00:22:32.640
A top cardiac specialist in the country

00:22:32.640 --> 00:22:35.360
is currently attending a conference
in Qingdao.

00:22:35.360 --> 00:22:38.679
He's agreed to help your classmate's father
with the surgery.

00:22:38.679 --> 00:22:39.840
Really?

00:22:39.840 --> 00:22:41.519
Thanks, Mom.

00:22:41.519 --> 00:22:42.719
Don't thank me.

00:22:42.719 --> 00:22:44.999
- You should thank the doctor.
- Okay.

00:22:45.920 --> 00:22:47.492
It's all settled.

00:22:48.320 --> 00:22:50.640
Lei Lei. Thank you.

00:22:50.640 --> 00:22:52.080
Thank you.

00:22:52.080 --> 00:22:53.560
- You're welcome.
- Thank you.

00:22:53.560 --> 00:22:55.519
No worries.

00:22:55.519 --> 00:22:57.519
Thanks.

00:23:04.160 --> 00:23:05.600
Alright, class.

00:23:05.600 --> 00:23:08.319
Time's up. Hand in your papers.

00:23:08.999 --> 00:23:11.519
Of course I'm done.
I checked it several times.

00:23:11.519 --> 00:23:14.039
I checked it, like, three times.

00:23:14.039 --> 00:23:15.120
I'll grab yours for you.

00:23:15.120 --> 00:23:16.920
How'd you do?

00:23:17.600 --> 00:23:19.080
It was all basic stuff.

00:23:19.080 --> 00:23:21.360
You just had to pay attention in class.

00:23:21.360 --> 00:23:22.633
Hurry, hurry.

00:23:22.633 --> 00:23:25.199
Xiao Ming. How did you do on the exam?

00:23:25.199 --> 00:23:27.519
It was okay, I guess.
At least I filled up the whole page.

00:23:27.519 --> 00:23:29.080
Fair enough.

00:23:29.080 --> 00:23:32.695
I wonder how Chen Ke's family is doing.

00:23:33.640 --> 00:23:35.360
I heard something happened
to Chen Ke's dad.

00:23:35.360 --> 00:23:37.640
Yu Lei didn't even take his final exams,
and went back with him.

00:23:37.640 --> 00:23:39.236
Tell me, isn't that true love?

00:23:39.236 --> 00:23:41.200
Totally.

00:23:41.200 --> 00:23:44.125
These days, all the handsome guys
end up with other handsome guys.

00:23:45.800 --> 00:23:47.279
Unbelievable.

00:23:47.279 --> 00:23:48.745
Right now, Yu Lei and Chen Ke

00:23:48.745 --> 00:23:51.160
probably have no idea
that they've been shipped as a couple.

00:23:51.160 --> 00:23:53.679
What's with students these days?

00:23:53.679 --> 00:23:56.560
Xiao Ming, wanna go shoot some hoops?

00:23:56.560 --> 00:23:58.360
To blow off some steam?

00:23:59.439 --> 00:24:01.040
Xiao Ming?

00:24:01.040 --> 00:24:02.892
- Xiao Ming?
- Xiao Ming?

00:24:02.892 --> 00:24:05.046
I have something to do. I'm heading out.

00:24:19.240 --> 00:24:20.360
Look at you.

00:24:20.360 --> 00:24:22.071
Eating like a bird over here?

00:24:22.719 --> 00:24:25.803
Better than some people
who only know how to stuff their face.

00:24:35.640 --> 00:24:38.320
Are you feeding a pig over there?

00:24:38.320 --> 00:24:39.600
I bought too much.

00:24:39.600 --> 00:24:41.400
Help me finish it.

00:24:50.039 --> 00:24:54.039
Anyway, the thing with Chen Ke and Yu Lei...

00:24:54.039 --> 00:24:56.239
Don't keep it bottled up.

00:24:56.239 --> 00:24:58.920
If you're feeling down about it,

00:24:58.920 --> 00:25:00.720
I'll play ball with you.

00:25:01.999 --> 00:25:03.469
You're being unusually nice.

00:25:03.469 --> 00:25:05.320
What are you up to?

00:25:05.320 --> 00:25:07.199
Aren't you on Yu Lei's side?

00:25:07.199 --> 00:25:08.999
Why do you care about me?

00:25:11.640 --> 00:25:15.479
I don't know why, but nowadays,

00:25:16.300 --> 00:25:19.188
I just can't stand seeing you unhappy.

00:25:32.813 --> 00:25:34.680
Why are you eating so fast?

00:25:35.640 --> 00:25:37.600
Didn't you say you wanted to play ball?

00:25:37.600 --> 00:25:39.240
Let's go.

00:25:39.240 --> 00:25:40.399
Not so fast.

00:25:40.399 --> 00:25:42.840
You can't exercise right after a full meal.

00:25:57.360 --> 00:26:00.800
Lei Lei. This scar on your neck...

00:26:00.800 --> 00:26:02.320
That's from when I was a kid.
I was climbing a tree,

00:26:02.320 --> 00:26:04.519
and I fell out of it.

00:26:04.519 --> 00:26:06.320
You've been a little rascal
since you were young.

00:26:06.320 --> 00:26:07.719
Nonsense.

00:26:07.719 --> 00:26:09.600
I wasn't the one who was fooling around.

00:26:09.600 --> 00:26:11.561
There was this other kid who got my toy

00:26:11.561 --> 00:26:12.999
stuck up in the tree.

00:26:12.999 --> 00:26:16.374
I was just trying to get it back,
so I climbed up.

00:26:16.374 --> 00:26:17.600
Lei Lei.

00:26:17.600 --> 00:26:21.360
Was it a model airplane?

00:26:21.999 --> 00:26:24.439
I think that might be right.

00:26:24.439 --> 00:26:25.800
It was in the summer, right?

00:26:25.800 --> 00:26:27.959
The model airplane was made of wood chips.

00:26:27.959 --> 00:26:29.560
You were spending summer vacation
at your aunt's house.

00:26:29.560 --> 00:26:32.800
And before you left,
you even gave that plane to the other kid.

00:26:32.800 --> 00:26:34.799
How did you know that?

00:26:49.759 --> 00:26:52.039
- Bye.
- Bye.

00:26:54.039 --> 00:26:55.560
It was you.

00:26:55.560 --> 00:26:56.999
That other kid was you.

00:26:56.999 --> 00:26:59.039
Lei Lei. That boy was you?

00:26:59.039 --> 00:27:03.160
Honey, what's going on here?

00:27:03.160 --> 00:27:04.239
You don't remember?

00:27:04.239 --> 00:27:08.799
He's the little boy that our Chen Ke
used to play with.

00:27:10.120 --> 00:27:11.999
So it was you.

00:27:11.999 --> 00:27:14.000
That kid, Ke Ke... After that day,

00:27:14.000 --> 00:27:15.640
he kept talking about you
for the longest time.

00:27:15.640 --> 00:27:19.320
After my aunt moved away,
I never came back here.

00:27:19.320 --> 00:27:20.479
It's okay.

00:27:20.479 --> 00:27:22.720
We've met again in college, haven't we?

00:27:22.720 --> 00:27:25.239
That's what you call fate.

00:27:26.039 --> 00:27:27.039
Yeah.

00:27:27.039 --> 00:27:29.629
Now that you mention it, after you left,

00:27:29.629 --> 00:27:32.679
Ke Ke cried quite a few times at home.

00:27:32.679 --> 00:27:35.519
I... I'm not that much of a crybaby.

00:27:35.519 --> 00:27:37.439
Oh, yes you were. You cried so hard.

00:27:37.439 --> 00:27:40.320
Even your piano playing was all choppy.

00:27:40.320 --> 00:27:42.120
Mom...

00:27:42.120 --> 00:27:45.120
Ke Ke, you're not a crybaby,

00:27:45.120 --> 00:27:50.239
but I clearly remember
every single time you've cried.

00:27:50.239 --> 00:27:52.039
There's no way I'm wrong.

00:27:52.039 --> 00:27:53.920
Yeah.

00:27:55.519 --> 00:27:57.999
So you missed me that much.

00:28:37.640 --> 00:28:39.560
You, student. Stand up.

00:28:39.560 --> 00:28:41.360
What's going on?

00:28:42.120 --> 00:28:44.640
- This isn't mine.
- This cheat sheet was right next to you.

00:28:44.640 --> 00:28:46.080
If it's not yours, whose is it?

00:28:46.080 --> 00:28:47.439
I don't know.

00:28:47.439 --> 00:28:48.600
You really don't know?

00:28:48.600 --> 00:28:50.600
I really don't.

00:28:50.600 --> 00:28:52.880
Professor, I can vouch for him.

00:28:52.880 --> 00:28:54.560
That note isn't his.

00:28:54.560 --> 00:28:55.600
Are you sure?

00:28:55.600 --> 00:28:57.279
I'm sure.

00:28:57.279 --> 00:28:58.600
I'm sitting right behind him.

00:28:58.600 --> 00:29:02.479
That piece of paper
floated over from the front.

00:29:02.479 --> 00:29:04.439
But I'm sure it's not his.

00:29:04.439 --> 00:29:07.160
Alright. Sit down for now.

00:29:21.160 --> 00:29:23.360
Alright, time's up. Hand in your papers.

00:29:23.360 --> 00:29:25.120
Let's go.

00:29:25.120 --> 00:29:26.920
Hand it in.

00:29:27.800 --> 00:29:29.920
- Stop writing, let's go.
- Alright, alright.

00:29:29.920 --> 00:29:32.640
Hey, man. Hand this in for me.

00:29:35.080 --> 00:29:36.880
Let's go.

00:29:39.880 --> 00:29:41.160
Hey.

00:29:41.160 --> 00:29:42.439
Thanks.

00:29:42.439 --> 00:29:44.080
For what?

00:29:44.080 --> 00:29:45.880
I didn't see anything.

00:29:46.640 --> 00:29:48.430
Then why did you...

00:29:49.320 --> 00:29:52.560
I just figured that
even with all your faults,

00:29:52.560 --> 00:29:55.720
you wouldn't stoop to cheating.

00:29:56.920 --> 00:29:59.640
Explain yourself. What kind of person am I?

00:29:59.640 --> 00:30:01.800
You're...

00:30:01.800 --> 00:30:04.560
all brawn, no brains.

00:30:04.560 --> 00:30:06.002
I...

00:30:07.120 --> 00:30:11.479
Are you complimenting me or insulting me?

00:30:12.199 --> 00:30:16.920
But, you're still pretty reliable.

00:30:21.560 --> 00:30:23.960
What are you doing? You big gorilla.

00:30:23.960 --> 00:30:25.106
Hey, listen.

00:30:25.959 --> 00:30:28.600
In a few days, they're airing the Olympic bid
live at the city plaza.

00:30:28.600 --> 00:30:30.840
We should go together.

00:30:30.840 --> 00:30:32.479
Who wants to go with you?

00:30:32.479 --> 00:30:33.999
It'll be so crowded.

00:30:33.999 --> 00:30:38.680
Besides, it'll end so late.
Where would we even stay?

00:30:39.959 --> 00:30:41.160
We can stay at a hotel.

00:30:41.160 --> 00:30:43.800
It's not like we haven't
stayed in one before.

00:30:51.160 --> 00:30:53.199
When this IV bag is empty,
remember to call the nurse.

00:30:53.199 --> 00:30:54.999
Okay, thank you.

00:31:01.679 --> 00:31:05.239
Lei Lei, at school,

00:31:05.239 --> 00:31:08.960
are you and Ke Ke the best of friends?

00:31:09.880 --> 00:31:12.239
I... I guess so.

00:31:12.239 --> 00:31:14.960
Ke Ke doesn't have any siblings.

00:31:15.679 --> 00:31:19.920
And he doesn't have any other close friends.

00:31:19.920 --> 00:31:22.959
Seeing you by his side, keeping him company,

00:31:22.959 --> 00:31:25.519
I'm really happy for him.

00:31:25.519 --> 00:31:28.479
Sir, actually, Chen Ke is a great guy.

00:31:28.479 --> 00:31:30.199
A lot of people at school like him.

00:31:30.199 --> 00:31:32.640
It's true. You don't have to worry.

00:31:34.800 --> 00:31:37.039
When he was growing up,

00:31:37.039 --> 00:31:39.719
I was only focused on my business.

00:31:39.719 --> 00:31:42.360
I thought that as long as I made money,

00:31:42.360 --> 00:31:46.400
I could provide for him and his mother.

00:31:47.360 --> 00:31:53.039
But, you see the situation now.

00:31:53.039 --> 00:31:58.160
This kid, he's become more and more
distant with me.

00:31:58.160 --> 00:32:02.120
Sir, actually, Chen Ke does care about you.

00:32:02.120 --> 00:32:03.609
It's just that,

00:32:03.609 --> 00:32:07.719
I think it's because you two
haven't had a good talk in a long time.

00:32:07.719 --> 00:32:10.759
If you were willing to sit down
and really talk,

00:32:10.759 --> 00:32:13.640
maybe things aren't as bad as you think.

00:32:15.600 --> 00:32:19.719
It's my own body.
I know it better than anyone.

00:32:19.719 --> 00:32:22.160
You're all just trying to humor me,

00:32:22.160 --> 00:32:25.640
saying that after this surgery,
I'll be all better.

00:32:25.640 --> 00:32:29.040
Actually, I know you're just
trying to make me feel better.

00:32:29.800 --> 00:32:33.999
There's no such thing as a risk-free surgery.

00:32:33.999 --> 00:32:38.199
Sir, the lead surgeon this time is an expert.

00:32:38.199 --> 00:32:40.160
Everything will go smoothly for you.

00:32:40.160 --> 00:32:41.788
Really.

00:32:42.640 --> 00:32:49.120
Lei Lei, I can tell, you're a good kid.

00:32:49.120 --> 00:32:55.679
I have no other wish than for you
to always be by Ke Ke's side,

00:32:55.679 --> 00:32:57.479
staying as such good friends.

00:32:57.479 --> 00:33:04.880
Together with his mother,
please continue to be there for him.

00:33:09.279 --> 00:33:11.800
Sir, don't overthink things.

00:33:11.800 --> 00:33:14.320
You're going to get better very soon.

00:33:14.320 --> 00:33:16.479
I promise.

00:33:16.479 --> 00:33:17.920
Sir, don't worry.

00:33:17.920 --> 00:33:19.519
No matter what happens in the future,

00:33:19.519 --> 00:33:22.444
I will always be there for Chen Ke.

00:33:22.444 --> 00:33:25.079
I'll treat him like my own brother.

00:33:41.520 --> 00:33:44.235
[In Operation]

00:33:47.999 --> 00:33:50.239
Why isn't he out yet?

00:33:50.239 --> 00:33:52.160
It's okay.

00:33:58.519 --> 00:34:01.239
Director Wang, how is my husband doing?

00:34:01.239 --> 00:34:03.600
You are the patient's family, right?

00:34:03.600 --> 00:34:05.360
Well, don't worry.

00:34:05.360 --> 00:34:07.439
The surgery went very smoothly.

00:34:07.439 --> 00:34:09.319
It was a success.

00:34:10.320 --> 00:34:12.760
Doctor, but why isn't my dad out yet?

00:34:12.760 --> 00:34:14.599
Don't get worked up.

00:34:14.599 --> 00:34:16.519
Our colleagues are in there,

00:34:16.519 --> 00:34:18.079
they need to run some checks on him.

00:34:18.079 --> 00:34:20.240
Think about it,
he needs to regain consciousness

00:34:20.240 --> 00:34:22.280
before we can feel at ease
about sending him to the ward.

00:34:22.280 --> 00:34:24.280
Otherwise, something could go wrong.

00:34:24.280 --> 00:34:26.840
So, it's going to take a little time.

00:34:26.840 --> 00:34:29.760
You all just need to wait a bit longer.

00:34:29.760 --> 00:34:30.480
Thank you, thank you.

00:34:30.480 --> 00:34:32.880
Ke Ke, thank goodness you helped me
make the decision

00:34:32.880 --> 00:34:34.959
of not rushing into transferring hospitals.

00:34:34.959 --> 00:34:37.959
Lei Lei, thank you.

00:34:37.959 --> 00:34:40.800
Thank you for helping our family so much.

00:34:40.800 --> 00:34:42.079
Thank you.

00:34:42.079 --> 00:34:43.840
Ke Ke is my best friend.

00:34:43.840 --> 00:34:46.039
I treat him like my own brother.

00:34:46.039 --> 00:34:48.360
I'd do anything for him.

00:34:48.360 --> 00:34:49.320
Thank you.

00:34:49.320 --> 00:34:51.680
Mom, now that we're past this hurdle,

00:34:51.680 --> 00:34:54.000
Dad is definitely going to get better.

00:35:03.119 --> 00:35:05.560
Oh, right. Look at this.

00:35:07.159 --> 00:35:08.959
Where did you get these?

00:35:08.959 --> 00:35:11.639
My dad said the doctors worked really hard
on the surgery,

00:35:11.639 --> 00:35:13.600
so we should show our appreciation.

00:35:13.600 --> 00:35:17.600
But it turns out,
they don't accept gifts at all.

00:35:17.600 --> 00:35:20.240
Anyway, since your uncle's surgery
was a success,

00:35:20.240 --> 00:35:21.160
let's try them.

00:35:21.160 --> 00:35:23.080
Let's unwind a bit.

00:35:23.080 --> 00:35:24.177
Here.

00:35:24.177 --> 00:35:25.640
Do you know how to smoke?

00:35:25.640 --> 00:35:27.879
How hard can it be?

00:35:37.039 --> 00:35:39.359
Wait. This tastes awful.

00:35:39.359 --> 00:35:41.927
Why do adults even smoke?

00:35:47.200 --> 00:35:50.079
I don't think we know how to do this.
We should just stop.

00:35:50.079 --> 00:35:51.280
Let's go get something to eat.

00:35:51.280 --> 00:35:53.160
Okay.

00:35:53.160 --> 00:35:56.279
Look at you. You're tearing up.

00:35:59.840 --> 00:36:01.760
Ke Ke.

00:36:01.760 --> 00:36:06.240
If you need someone to hold, you can hold me.

00:36:06.240 --> 00:36:08.319
You don't have to be strong.

00:36:17.519 --> 00:36:18.680
It's okay now.

00:36:18.680 --> 00:36:19.840
Ke Ke.

00:36:19.840 --> 00:36:22.080
It's really okay now.

00:36:22.720 --> 00:36:25.120
I know.

00:36:25.120 --> 00:36:27.159
I know.

00:36:27.879 --> 00:36:31.879
It's just... I'm still so shaken.

00:36:33.359 --> 00:36:34.680
I was so scared.

00:36:34.680 --> 00:36:38.079
What if I'd made the wrong decision?

00:36:38.079 --> 00:36:40.359
What if...

00:36:40.359 --> 00:36:42.879
What if the surgery had failed?

00:36:42.879 --> 00:36:44.034
July 15th.

00:36:44.034 --> 00:36:46.479
- What if my dad...
- Sunny.

00:36:46.479 --> 00:36:48.519
Many people are probably still basking in

00:36:48.519 --> 00:36:51.879
the afterglow of Beijing's
successful Olympic bid.

00:36:51.879 --> 00:36:56.520
As for us, we're celebrating
Dad's new lease on life.

00:36:57.640 --> 00:37:00.999
Life is truly full of uncertainties.

00:37:00.999 --> 00:37:06.600
While in Yu Lei's arms,
I was thinking, if one day,

00:37:06.600 --> 00:37:09.120
I were to suddenly die too,

00:37:09.120 --> 00:37:13.240
what place would I hold in Yu Lei's heart?

00:37:13.240 --> 00:37:16.680
Yu Lei probably thinks
that being "brothers"

00:37:16.680 --> 00:37:19.200
is the closest relationship we can have.

00:37:19.200 --> 00:37:21.600
But for a long time now,

00:37:21.600 --> 00:37:24.440
I've wanted to be more than just brothers.

00:37:24.440 --> 00:37:26.588
[Next Episode]
It must be He Jin.

00:37:26.588 --> 00:37:27.480
I'm going to settle the score with him.

00:37:27.480 --> 00:37:30.320
But if you hit him,
you'll be the one who gets in trouble.

00:37:30.320 --> 00:37:31.439
Yeah.

00:37:31.439 --> 00:37:32.680
I did it all.

00:37:32.680 --> 00:37:34.600
So what?

00:37:34.600 --> 00:37:36.517
It's all of you.

00:37:36.517 --> 00:37:38.920
One after another, you all look down on me.

00:37:38.920 --> 00:37:42.973
You only earn respect
by acting with integrity.

00:37:42.973 --> 00:37:44.974
You blame everyone else for your problems.

00:37:44.974 --> 00:37:47.080
Why don't you look at yourself for once?

00:37:47.080 --> 00:37:49.643
Ke Ke, no matter what happens in the future,

00:37:49.643 --> 00:37:51.588
I'll always be by your side.

00:37:51.588 --> 00:37:53.894
A lifetime?

00:37:53.894 --> 00:37:55.759
That's so unrealistic.